The package boost-callable-traits is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS callable_traits)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::callable_traits)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_callable_traits REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::callable_traits)
